Package: webforest
Title: Web-Native Interactive Forest Plots
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Antoine", "Baldassari", , "baldassarian@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Antoine Baldassari [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Antoine Baldassari <baldassarian@gmail.com>
Description: Create interactive, web-native forest plots and tables. Forest plots
    visualize point estimates with intervals for any domain: meta-analysis,
    regression results, QC measurements, and more. Rendered using modern web
    technologies (Svelte, D3.js) for R Markdown, Quarto, Shiny, and standalone
    HTML. Features include collapsible groups, customizable columns, sorting,
    filtering, and rich theming.
